{"tid":1671226,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"彭博：香港警方擁有人臉識別軟件　未知有否在近月示威使用","createTime":"2019-10-23T10:44:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-23T11:23:27.000Z","uid":259088,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"17e36e6aaed8d8d740cc998b29dac81320dc9c79","tid":1671226,"uid":259088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T10:44:49.000Z","msg":"《彭博通訊社》引述知情人士報道，香港警方擁有具人臉識別功能的人工智能軟件，但不清楚有無在近月的反修例示威中使用。<br />\n<br />\n報道說，警方最少3年前已經使用澳洲悉尼一間公司的人工智能技術，軟件可以透過掃描包括閉路電視在內的畫面，與警方的資料庫比對，自動識別人臉及車牌，在人群中找出疑犯。有關公司派人為香港警員提供培訓，有警員在6月反修例示威爆發後，詢問如何利用行車記錄儀畫面，自動識別車牌。<br />\n<br />\n《彭博》向有關澳洲公司查詢是否有向警方提供人臉識別技術，未獲正面回應，本港警方亦未有回覆是否有使用相關技術。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1487800-20191023.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1487800-20191023.htm&d=krzUv%2FzG327U7XiGlMZ3yID442Ur5281Gkz3GsmHlD8%3D&h=15830e4a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1487800-20191023.htm&h=8766d6eb\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1487800-20191023.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n網上有其他報道指該澳洲公司是<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">iOmniscient</span></strong>"},{"pid":"fe25652c3c281978232985071785292cfda3a346","tid":1671226,"uid":35456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T10:48:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5ec4ee7661f3c974358026db0d990dae02e8c274","tid":1671226,"uid":35456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T10:48:18.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"bf0ea28694740ccc98094b56a2cd8c5ecb2392a6","tid":1671226,"uid":249263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T10:54:55.000Z","msg":"Twitter<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n今日task2 <br />\n有nba 賽事有人 派Stand with Hong Kong T shirt <br />\n仲有Senatorsssss講中共對美國威脅<br />\n得幾百Retweet rate<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hk